In need for speed: The Run it competes across America.
Overview
A trip, in principle carefree, is complicated because of a series of improper omissions of a routine trip during the morning.
To some extent they managed to meet expectations, but it is no use, if, in fact, it was not intended to do anything extraordinary.
The new delivery, which is added to the title The Run, awakened great expectations even before its premiere.
New promised to give up the old saga of careers need for speed and, as a result of the show, appears as a game that should not end up being another kind of action.
We are also curious to know how the scenes would be inserted, where the main character is descended from the car and walk on his foot.
As is often the case in the series of NFS, the results will not vary much about what we had hoped.
There are careers that can be taken by acceptable, but the total lost points because of failures absurd, which are already appearing in the series for years.
In reality cannot be or call mistakes, but it is more about the unwillingness of programmers incomprehensible.
The adventure begins very well.
Beneficiaries.35 is introduced in a story, whose protagonist, Jack, has some personal problems; to solve them, he offers to participate in an illegal race across America.
Os sentáis at the wheel on the west coast, in San Francisco, and your mission is to get the first to New York.
The idea is to offer something interesting.
The route is divided into 10 stages and then, in more than 50 careers.
It follows that every race takes place on a different route and the stages are located in different environments, which are quite different and interesting.
That way, one is not remotely the feeling that the game offers is always the same.
Some are even pleasant environments in sight, although the technical level of the figure is equivalent to that of previous rendition of the series.
Therefore, it is nothing of another world.
But the walk in the desert, the autumn landscape or the high mountains covered in snow produced a very pleasant visual effect.
, is racing to diversify from time to time by an atypical element.
So, for example, in the desert beneficiaries.35 encontráis a storm of sand that diminishes visibility.
In contrast, in the mountains we must be careful not to beneficiaries.35 sepulte an avalanche.
According to this, each of the racing is very well developed.
There are only a couple of models, but this is enough.
For a time, intentáis advance to a number of rivals demanded (as normal in a classic race), after whom to gain time (classic duel timed) and then you expected a duel against a single opponent.
In the midst of all this is sometimes the police, but that does not make things even more difficult.
Novelty are the landscape outside the car.
When Jack interactive animations are, in most cases, has to escape from someone and you have to help him, provided by clicking the button at the right time.
Nothing complicated.
It is surprising, however, that there are fewer landscapes in the game of what might be expected (in particular, there are only three).
But the end result is positive, because this element is not to be disturbed and, in the context already mentioned, is one of the elements that make the game more interesting.
The model is driving the fingerprints of the previous episodes.
This means that today is no longer a big deal, but you cannot say that it is bad.
If buscáis a realistic simulation, because you can look elsewhere.
But in a race designed with enough action suits rather this style of driving, although we can find something better between games of competition.
So far, all in order.
But the problems arise after a certain time.
Unlike the right models of driving, because this is not the case with collisions.
Games of this kind cannot expect recreated with deformities and collisions complicated, but in fact before a coup against any object, you cannot predict how they will react to your car, so that not everything is in order.
It is typical that, to make a very tight overtaking or move the car with a normal traffic, has only slight friction, but in other situations almost identical, your car just doing gymnastics uncontrolled.
Or even just totally destroyed.
Thanks to the system of reseteo, no major problems arise, but may settle your differences now in a bad mood.
The reseteos are scheduled in such a way that, when you suffer an accident or you salt of the runway, the game you rescue restores the last point on the runway.
However, in every race is available only five reseteos available.
If the consumís all, you have to restart the race from the outset.
So it is no more than a help in the event that something is not going well, but it is not very reliable.
Sometimes, nor the reseteo aid, only learned the aid of the stage in memory.
A big disadvantage of the game is that the same facts are repeated in different places.
In some curves, for example, is to enter a specific way; otherwise, are impossible to take.
Other times you encontráis somewhere vehicles "civilian" always with the same configuration, even if you are the first, fifth or lleguéis five minutes sooner or later.
This makes rabiar especially in situations, when VEIS that two cars that are going to the meeting in opposite directions, your opponent is without problems, but when you, you must be either curb.
It is like when lleguéis, because it is scheduled for the "surprise" always happen in front of your nose.
The opponents also have an advantage.
Throughout the game llegaréis to places where, without taking into account the time, you are always at the same opponent in the same place.
Furthermore this happens at the end of the game, in a long bridge, which is even more shocking.
Your opponent must come before you, whatever the cost.
When it is in front of you, you makes the vision of cars that come from front, so that you can make porridge to start the car.
You can understand the idea of creating a game with maximum dose of suspense and adrenaline, but the execution is so apparent that surely disappoint you immediately.
And it is a pity, because although the model of the journey is simple, the game is fun and action, so often it is not possible to continue to detail what happens or where.
And really gives equal, if the credit takes the idea with 50 clues exclusive or the classification in the race to avoid boredom, or anything else.
An unusual idea is the change of cars during the careers.
You must be alert to the petrol pumps at the side of the road, because then you must change their car, although in the vast majority of cases you what you will suffice.
Cars are divided into three categories.
The sports are suitable for urban areas, strong American cars for motorways and the exotic superdeportivos straight for a driving technique, for example, on mountain roads with curves.
In addition to main narrative thread is also a thread of challenges parallel, i.e., racing in specific locations that are known for the stories.
Conseguiréis here not only medals, but also points to experience for your profile, which serves both to the challenges as the tales.
To reach the highest level, the driver he opened several possibilities, starting with the car and ending with funds to the profile.
At the same time, there are connected a role Autolog online, which compares your results with those of other players and other Community disponibiliza functions.
One of the most difficult to understand is how it is made the last race in history.
With the car you until the subway tunnel (pass), where beneficiaries.35 ponéis to run in the dark on the tracks (go).
The os marks a speedometer between 150 and 200 km/h (go) and, suddenly, you get behind the convoy subway and goes ahead without further.
In the drafting may have a discussion about this for several days, whether during the programming of the game a little or none thought even if the authors we really taken by a bunch of stupid crooks.
The technical side of the game is nothing extraordinary, but at least the general visual effects are in the majority of cases, pleasant, sometimes so impressive.
Because what a pity that, in the most tense moments it reduces the quality of image and, at times, in a serious way.
This particularly affects accidents where there are many players involved, when the quality of continuous image is no longer valid.
The audio is good and the soundtrack is a matter of taste.
In order to make the most of the youth group, the soundtrack belongs to the category "each of his father and his mother," but you can assume that anyone would buy the game only for his music.
The final sense of need for speed: The Run is therefore quite confused.
If the game to avoid mistakes absolutely stupid, we would have problems in saying that The Run is the best game of NFS in recent years.
Gives the feeling that the game is not over.
The fun is insured, but preparaos because the mistakes will attack you in the eyes with the force of a spotlight on airport.
The choirs of Charles University will participate in the concert "Velvet Students."
The joint celebration of the International Day of Students and the anniversary of the Velvet Revolution as musical experience will take place for the third time in the festival Festa Academy.
During the same, there will be 20 bleaching of secondary and university students.
The festival revolves around two concerts on 17 November.
"The Carolina University has a high turnout in the festival."
Among the current choirs are the coral in the Faculty of pedagogy and the Faculty of Arts, the committee of the festival is the rector Václav Hampl, "said the head of the organisation, Jakub Čaloun.
The summit of the festival is free entry for all the public to the concert of the secondary Choir, which will be held on March 17 to 14 hours in front of the National Technical hook in Dejvice.
The programme with the participation of the Czech Karel Růžička jazzista and its Celebration Jazz mass.
By the evening will be held at the venues of the Municipal House in Vynohrady the concert "Velvet Students," involving university corals, including the chorus of the Carolina Uninversidad.
The Festa Academy is intended not only to celebrate a decent International Students Day and remember the 22nd anniversary of the Velvet Revolution, but also to present to the public the choral music at the highest level and promote collaborative creation among young people.
The main organizer is the Czech Union coral in collaboration with the Institute of Higher Jan Kepler.
All acts had the support of the mayor of Prague, Bohuslav Svoboda, and rector of the University of Carolina, Václav Hampl.
The Festival will be between 16 and 20 November between Prague and Pardubice.
The calendar offers, in addition to the concerts celebrativos, a whole series of musical events, improvised performances of students and morning concerts.
Interested parties can find more information on the festival www.festaacademica.cz
The ambassador to the EU, Vicenová:
The Czechs have a reputation for manifestly and Eurosceptics.
"The Lisbon treaty has significantly affected the balance between individual institutions'
"I had hoped that montase a merciless war."
"Will last five, six years before the situation has stabilised somewhat, calming and the new players to become accustomed to their new roles," so he began with conviction its conference in the Faculty of Law, the Czech ambassador to the EU, Milena Vicenová.
How does not take seriously its motto "clearly and openly about Europe," he said in the first part of the conference, when managed to describe each body of the EU and its relations with such precision and clarity, because it would be the envy of many speakers of the Faculty of Law of the Carolina Ulrich.
Vicenová also commended the work of the new permanent president of the European Council, Herman van Rompuy:
"The first arise criticism, that if it is bland, an official grey, capable of taking any role, but I have to say that left all confused, because it takes its role to perfection."
"He is a man who knows how to listen to the members of the 27 states, communicate with them and that has a clear vision of where the EU should go."
The new post of representative of the Common Foreign and Security stems from the question: "Who is this ΕU? What number can call it? 'Because it is an important step towards the unification and clarification of the political union for states such as China or India.
Nobody wants to prevent us from the cheese Olomouc
Vicenová has also dealt with the agenda was, is and will continue to the European Council in the near future.
The Czech presidency of two years ago was a success.
The Czechs were emerging from the economic crisis, resolved the gas crisis and held a summit for the Eastern Partnership.
The fall of the government at the time was identified as a very negative aspect, which seriously affected the Czech Republic.
The Czech representation in the EU has for the moment many commitments.
In the words of the ambassador: "A good fuss," not only the presidency, but also the financial crisis, which is now being treated.
On the other hand, we must approve the budget for seven years in the EU, caused by the current economic situation, much more complicated.
If the budget is more simple and effective, what will have priority sectors, which countries will receive more support and less? This is something that will be on the agenda of the next meeting.
The ambassador also recalled its main slogans, with those who came to Europe: "About Europe with clarity."
"The truth is that I do not like the abbreviations Ugly, the extranjerismos or the jargon that people do not understand."
"How can a citizen to understand that in Brussels is not fabricate really cucumbers cucumbers or curved free round, plátanos of various sizes or that nobody is going to ban the Olomouc cheese?".
It also aims to get more of the atmosphere of the EU and bring more Czech citizens to the European institutions.
We expect Europe of the speeds
According to the ambassador, the Czechs have a reputation of Eurosceptics and people perceived rather negative aspects that the positive.
Also regretted the low turnout of the Czechs in the European institutions.
The fault lies with a multitude of factors, such as the modesty of our candidates, their inability to write messages of motivation, but also the little support for the Czechs.
In addition to the success of the Czech Presidency, underscored the strength and the cooperation of the Visegrad Group.
"Believe me when I go to a Polish and Hungarian and I was on a Slovak, a Frenchman in my hand, I said:" What, you have already left, those of the Visegrad Group?, "and you see that there is no laughing."
In the future, the EU, according to Vicenová, faces new regulations harsh budgetary policy for the Member States.
It is perceived as something very real the concept of the two speeds, if not more, in Europe, more than the new "European Federation."
"We need countries in the eurozone and countries outside the euro zone."
"We have the Schengen area and we also have the enhanced cooperation procedure."
"Said for the first time that only those countries that want to cooperate and those who do not, to be left out."
"These procedures will be increasingly and strengthen the two-speed Europe", is expected Vicenová.
In this sense, also stressed the role of the Czech Republic and Herman van Rompuy in the application of the principle, according to which all the issues that affect the entirety of the EU should be discussed between the member states, not just between the members of the eurozone.
Brand story:
The innovative IBM enters its second century of existence
If you seek a term defined with great precision the strategy of IBM, the clearest would be "long term."
For the general public, IBM is the symbol of a technological revolution, a company that is perceived as current and, however, have already passed 100 years since its founding.
The basis of this character largoplacista the became the first head of the signing, the visionary Thomas J. Watson.
Because he coined the slogan that many of the world's problems can be solved if people are willing to think.
Its slogan "Think!" Became his trademark, around which will build the life of the future (giant was also the title of a magazine that IBM internal began publishing in 1935).
Watson was also the basis of a culture of company carefully lifted.
"For us, IBM involves a long-term thinking, a continuous movement in the direction of the future.
IBM has survived and prospered over 100 years for that reason, because remained faithful to its basic principles, but without fear the changes around.
This has enabled us during our first century, transforming technology, business and society.
Hope prosper even more in our second century, "said during its anniversary, the current director of the company, Samuel J. Palmisano.
A sophisticated system
Watson, as in the 1930s, took care of their employees as the employer of Baťa in the Czech Republic (IBM employees were among the first American who enjoyed operators paid vacation, sure, elegant uniforms and a sophisticated system of remuneration that rewards the best inventors and sellers.
The same sophistication in the long term keeps IBM in the relationship with the customer.
Right from the beginning, the company was able to discover talents (to be one of the first global companies ending any kind of discrimination, could choose without problems).
In line with the anti-discrimination strategy is the current plan of IBM, which Palmisano to replace him next year a woman: Virginia Rometty.
She has been working 30 years at IBM, where he has been head of sales, márquetin and strategies.
During the past few years, IBM has participated in the so-called virtual meetings, rain of ideas online, of which there are countless future strategies and innovations.
It is no surprise that allowed ideas, because in the signature work almost half a million people.
An institution with good reputation
The fixed position in the business gives the company a strong internal and external image.
"From the beginning, IBM held a concept of institution rather than technology company," says the economist professor at the Harvard Business School and author of the book on IBM Rosabeth Moss Kanter.
"IBM is not a technology company, but a company that tries to solve business problems for users of technology," said George colony of the consultancy Forrester Research.
As the company itself says there is a difference between going into the business and create a business.
IBM - or the "Great Green" - as it is affectionately known in the US because of its logo, has become the last hundred years in one of the largest companies in the world.
It is possibly the most versatile technology company (develops both hardware and software, infrastructure and services accommodation website within a wide range of services, ranging from servers to nanotechnology).
Holds the largest number of patents of all American technology companies and five of their employees have received the Nobel Prize.
Among their inventions are the cash dispenser, payment cards, the swaps, the bar codes and diskettes.
IBM billed this year 220 billion dollars. This year has become the second technology firm by market capitalisation (the first is Apple), when for the first time Microsoft in 1996.
The future looking
Not all products and innovations have just to satisfy the taste of customers and the time (IBM not opted for its own operating system, os/2, online services Prodigy or computers IBM PCjr).
"If your business is based in advance, cannot emotionally anchored in the past," acknowledged Samuel J. Palmisano.
Therefore, IBM has no problems in building their bases in other platforms (and equally, if they do not work, the leaves).
And this is the difference of competition, Microsoft, which basically is and always falls exclusively with Windows.
Of future technology
In terms of sales, IBM is devoted primarily to services, of which about one-fifth of programmes and one fifth of equipment.
However, even in 1990 equipment accounted for more than half of the quota of suppliers.
From the year 2000, IBM has sold low-yielding assets with a total value of $15 billion. During the same period, has invested $58 billion in the purchase of technology in the future.
Investments have followed since 2008, when for the first time was the modern global financial crisis.
IBM acts according to the premises of his first boss, Thomas J. Watson, who during the great economic crisis of 29 increased investments.
It seems that until now the company IBM has managed to weather the crisis.
The value of the shares of IBM since the start of 2008 has grown estratosféricamente up to 120%, the net profit of the company has continued to increase.
The currency of IBM is change everything, except its value.
Can therefore expect that when the next crisis comes, this giant aguantará flexible.
IBM history: From the cutters of cheese until space flights
The company IBM (International Business Machines) was founded in New York a hundred years ago, with its original name Computing Tabulating Recording Corporation.
The name IBM already adopted in the year 1924 - originally was a brand used in branches of Canada and South America.
The basis that resulted in the birth of IBM stems from the merger of four companies that date back to 1880's.
Possessed inventions such as the famous "clock out," which allows us to control the entry and exit of employees.
The architect of the new company was the businessman Charles Ranlett Flint, who until 1930 also chaired its supervisory board.
Flint fichó at the head of a company in competition, Thomas J. Watson, to assist with the management of the company.
The new leader eclipsed the founder of IBM (the ideas remain the firm basis on which underpin the corporate culture and identity).
Watson led the company until the year 1952.
IBM, as its name indicates, began with the production and sale of all kinds of devices for business, from cutting meat and cheese until tills.
During the first four years that Watson ran the company, billing doubled in 9 million dollars and began the vast expansion of the company by the continents.
Watson was so crucial to the company, almost 40 years after taking the chair of the leader, was replaced by his son, Thomas Watson junior.
Under his direction, IBM began work on the development of artificial intelligence and developed the first programming language.
In the 1960s, the staff and the computers of IBM helped NASA to guide flights into space (to Mercury, Saturn and in 1969 the famous flight to the moon).
Meanwhile, in 1964 IBM developed the first generation of computers, the series IBM System/360.
The classics "pecés", which established the standard of computers at the time, came to the market with the IBM 5150 in 1981.
20 years later, IBM sold its production of computers to the Chinese company Lenovo, which, for its part, became part of the consulting firm Pricewaterhouse Coopers and began to offer a complete advice and high value-added services.
The strategy that has paid IBM these last three years is the concept Smarter Planet, i.e., "a smarter planet."
Its aim is to make a more rational use of technology, but have not yet been planned or areas has been improved the circumstances, for example, in regard to transport and the administration of cities.
For the commercial sector, IBM introduced not long ago the platform "Smart Commerce" that allows retailers to manage the business cycle.
IBM has a long history in this country.
Already in 1932 opened a branch in the then Czechoslovakia, the first country that took in Central and Eastern Europe.
Today, IBM ČR operates along the strategic center of outsourcing in Brno.
The headquarters for Central and Eastern Europe has is in Prague. Here, too, there is a world-renowned research team that works with voice recognition.
