After 72 days of belonging, the network's legal hold Casino granted a pardon to the brother of the mayor of Monterrey of the process that was followed by alleged blackmail
After 72 days remain imprisoned, Manuel Jonás Larrazábal will be released after the legal hold Casino YEN granted forgiveness before the Second Circuit Criminal Court, which is a process for blackmail against the brother of the mayor of Monterrey.
Following the attack at the Casino Royale, the owner of the Casino YEN, Sergio Gil García, issued a series of photographs and videos in which he allegedly Manuel Jonás demanded the payment of a fee for the economic council regiomontano operation allowed illegal betting the house.
After the public denunciation, the state Procuraduría opened criminal proceedings against the brother of mayor panista and September 2 was arrested and rooted for 30 days.
After four hours before the official of the Public Prosecutor 3 in property crime, was transferred to the House of arraigo 1, located in the Old Quarter of the capital of the state.
There remained over the 49 days following the dictársele a second order of establishment after the agent of the Public Ministry throw out the crimes of corruption and organised crime.
On 19 October was transferred to the prison of Cadereyta allegedly by blackmail with one and a half million pesos to the owners of the Casino Network; however, only stayed a few hours at the medium-security only because there were death threats against him.
The authorities allowed him to continue the trial held in the cells of St. Nicholas of the municipal Garza.
On 25 October arrest warrant was issued by the Secretary of the Second District Criminal Court, Jorge Yáñez, who said that almost two months of inquiries were found sufficient evidence to determine the guilt of Jonás, such as the recovery of 1.5 billion pesos to the representatives of the house of stakes in exchange for allowing the operation.
This Monday, the legal hold Casino Network, Victor Aldo García Gómez, came before the judge José Luis Pecina to seek forgiveness for the brother of the mayor regio; so that in the coming hours could regain their freedom.
During the legal diligence, the agent of the Public Ministry attached to the Court, Ramiro Arias, questioned whether to Garcia Gomez had been repaired the damage and who the partners of the house was betting that gave the pardon, although the lawyer tried to reserve the name.
On the basis of the record 197/2011 confers a legal pardon to Jonás Larrazábal and thereafter will not stand any complaint about the process that was still; and that it will require repair damage or punishment.
After the hearing to hold legal betting the house, near the 15:50 were ordered the immediate release of the Breton Larrazabal.
